title: Undekhi
overview: Show depicts the two aspects of the society - the power-drunk influential people who think they can get away with anything and the oppressed, subjected to years of torture, who finally decide to bring themselves to justice

tv.episodeOverview: Papaji is recovering from his injuries and has given up alcohol while Rinku is trying to revive the business. However, Teji has plans of her own which lead to tension and a power struggle in the family. Meanwhile, Ghosh is ridden with guilt after Koyal’s death and has become a recluse, as amysterious new entity emerges with a vendetta and a sinister plan to bring down the Atwals.
